{"tid":213985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港經濟只能靠地產而且只能愈來愈靠地產","createTime":"2017-04-23T13:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T02:01:12.000Z","uid":76310,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b25f21576ab63f3cd4dbf99373bdabf36a87aa","tid":213985,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"香港經濟只能靠地產而且只能愈來愈靠地產<br />\n<br />\n現在香港各行各業萎縮中，有些是因爲中國因素，有些是因為地價成本，有些是因為不思長進，有些是因為壟斷<br />\n<br />\n娛樂文化事業，收皮<br />\n體育，收皮<br />\n金融，萎縮<br />\n零售，萎縮<br />\n物流，萎縮<br />\n離岸貿易做廠，萎縮<br />\n專業服務，萎縮<br />\n<br />\n香港正苦開支年年不斷升，公務員人工福利，大白象利益輸送，新移民福利開支，退休公務員開支，退休人士開支等<br />\n開支不斷，但收入條水就收縮<br />\n變相只能靠賣貴地來支撐，而且愈來愈貴"},{"pid":"4324a4ebf534b60e45b49ee1cf70aeffed63a99c","tid":213985,"uid":79484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪就係叫食老本，好快爆煲"},{"pid":"ae7205708985f47e1d9f22ae4e4ed55219e74b5b","tid":213985,"uid":73410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"政府大部份收入靠賣地得返嚟<br />\n地產商高價買到塊地，咪起啲樓賣得更貴<br />\n即係最後將啲錢轉嫁畀市民，地産商中間撈盡啲油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c70fe02dab6c56249fd8f3a4d442cc3fa72ef5","tid":213985,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04c5e13601f65b3a1d3039cdf0c5fcf11187821d","tid":213985,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"然後會發現地產狗慢慢變成中資"},{"pid":"259272f9f01095bbc98b0db850c1b5f583764f6a","tid":213985,"uid":37465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8001a412ec65d8798c4415d3b2135e09c54f902","tid":213985,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T00:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>